com.b2international.snowowl.snomed

Interface Description

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, Component, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Inactivatable, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DescriptionImpl

    public interface Description
extends Component, Inactivatable
    Representation of a SNOMED CT description. This associates some human readable literal with a SNOMED CT concept that it describes.

    The following features are supported:

    • Language Code
    • Term
    • Concept
    • Type
    • Case Significance
    • Language Ref Set Members

    See Also:
    SnomedPackage.getDescription()
